Okay..so it's been awhile but i have alot to talk about...

class were probably going to have people come watch.
I'm pretty excited..BECAUSE I LOVE ACTING! But yeah
I've been so confused about my boy issues, Brian and i 
are so confused on what's going on bewteen us. One 
Min it seems like he likes me the next he seems like he doesnt
So weird..but the other night my friend Daniel who i use to
like came up from Tucson and me and him were out till 4 am
driving it was so much fun...but i don't know it seems like no guy 
is super interessted in me..I don't know maybe that's how every guy 
treats a girl. But today i was sitting at this assembly at school and this
guy and girl were holding hands and were so into eachother all i could think
about was Brian because that's how we were a few weeks ago. It sucks! 
I like him so much but no one understands me... 
I want to leave and get away from here as far as possible. I just feel like
I'm wearing a mask everytime im around someone...like i can't take that 
mask off and no one really knows who the real person is...No one cares.
I don't know i'm so confused with life its unreal

So today Britt was having cramps while we we're sitting outside of the school in our car, She
decided to go home because she didn't feel so well. Athough i was alone today at lunch, i wasn;t
bummed out like i usually would be. Like normally i was always stressing about being alone I
didn't like being alone. But today, it didn't bother me, Britt has her own life i have mine
at lunch i sat in the hallway and did homework, and then catched up on some reading in my
Acting book. I was finally independent for once. I think i didn't mind so much becuz of that
book, Every day i wake up i realize more and more that Acting is my passion and i have so much
motivation in doing it, It's shocking because, i haven't been thinking about boys alot
The only boys ive been thinking about is ADRIEN BRODY (Jess in case you' don't remember what he
looks like..Here he is.) and this guy Kyle at my school..who im sure doesn't know i
exist..i dont care though. You have to remember im going to be an Actress which means i won't have
time for Phoneix boys anyways.
But my day went pretty well today, The only thing that i kind of didn't like about my day was pe.
My tennis partner and i had to find another pair of partners to play tennis agianst and she picked this girl
I dont really like. Shes really fake so you can't really tell when shes being truthful and when shes being full
of it. But anyways i felt bad for my partner because shes kind of bigger and shes one of those girls who seems like
she'll do anything to fit in, anyways i just felt bad I hope some day she realizes SOMETIMES IT DOESN'T MATTER IF YOU
FIT IN. YOU DON'T ALWAYS HAVE TO JUMP ON THE BAN WAGON. Hopefully she ends up realzing that..becuz if not shes going to
be living a life where she always wants people to be happy with her and to be honest there is a time when people wont always
approve of what you do or accept you for you. But it doesnt matter what people think about you. That's what i have been realzing, your JOB IS TO PLEASE YOURSELF. BE HAPPY WITH YOU FOR WHO YOU ARE. You have to learn to live with yourself everyone is their own unique person and the sooner you realzie that the more you'll like life! And if theres something your not happy with change it. You just have to have motivation. Anything you set your mind to you can do!
There will always be a better day or a better path that will come along.

Man theres so much i want to write but i know if i write much more no one is going to read this. So i guess in my next entry ill write more. Until than...Love ya!
Soon to be Actress!
